I-I guess Barry hasn't
had a hit movie in a while.

587
00:39:28.132 --> 00:39:31.864
so Sasha's doing his new one.
so Barry owes Sasha a favor. so...

588
00:39:33.938 --> 00:39:36.908
I'm trying to start a
new career later in life.

589
00:39:36.975 --> 00:39:41.037
