the language for.

772
00:51:35.826 --> 00:51:37.337
Oh. my God. I sound
like a fucking idiot.

773
00:51:37.361 --> 00:51:39.023
No. no. That's...

774
00:51:42.800 --> 00:51:43.893
That's beautiful.

775
00:51:48.872 --> 00:51:50.431
I've had enough. I think.

